::DrillBit::

"An Alliance, great. We'll talk about this in the conferance room."
He then saw Killfest walk up. He was about to say something to him when
the alarms went off, and Ram-Jet asked why. He opened a comm.
"Dark Mouse, whats with the alarms?"
He kept looking at Ram-Jet. He had heard that name in his history tapes.
Could this be one of the 'seeker' Decepticons?
